## 📂 Next.js Directory & Architecture Rules
- Every Page or API handler must reside in the `src/app/` directory (App Router structure).
- Shared presentational components must be placed in `src/components/`.
- Maintain a strict division: Use Server Components for data fetching and keep Client Components (`'use client'`) lightweight and localized to specific interactive elements.